38) Ensure that the GPB and GAD AR are prepared, approved and submitted in accordance with PCW-DILG-DBM-NEDA JMC No. 2013-01, as amended by JMC No. 2016-01;
39) Establish and maintain a GAD Database; 
40) Assist in the formulation of GAD Code and other related ordinances; and
41) Establish a GAD Monitoring and Evaluation System.

